sec.p:
The final model developed for those with negative FOBT results only included; smoking status, sex, age at FOBT, previous negative BCSP FOBT results, blood test ordered by the GP and whether a patient has an IBS diagnosis. Age of FOBT was modelled using fractional polynomials and previous negative BSCP FOBT results was centred. The model is reported below in Table 3.
